cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on defending against trojan attacks on deep neural networks in the context of vision systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it deals with attacks and defenses against security threats. The paper also involves computer vision and machine learning techniques, making cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) likely categories as well.
